# Ignore Liquid Variables and placeholders (escaped for Lychee regex engine)
\{\{.*\}\}
\{%.*\%\}
\{\{\s*base_path\s*\}\}
\{\{\s*site\.baseurl\s*\}\}
\{\{\s*post\.link\s*\}\}

# Ignore common social media placeholders with variables
https://www\.linkedin\.com/in/\{\{.*\}\}
https://twitter\.com/\{\{.*\}\}
https://github\.com/\{\{.*\}\}
https://www\.facebook\.com/\{\{.*\}\}
https://www\.instagram\.com/\{\{.*\}\}

# Ignore 429 errors (Too Many Requests) from platforms that block scrapers
https://www\.instagram\.com/.*
https://www\.linkedin\.com/.*
https://twitter\.com/.*

# Ignore specific broken legacy links confirmed in logs
https://api\.staticman\.net/v1/entry/.*
https://www\.youtube\.com/watch\?v=O_HyZ5aW76c

# Ignore system directories (though the workflow now scans _site)
_includes/
_layouts/
_sass/
/Users/.*
